title: RAK12059 WisBlock Liquid Level Sensor > RAK12059 WisBlock Liquid Level Sensor > Product Description > RAK12059 WisBlock Liquid Level Sensor Overview
content: RAK12059 is a WisBlock Liquid Level Sensor module that extends the WisBlock system with a Liquid Level Sensor from MILONE. It comes with a ready-to-use software library and tutorial, making it easy to build a liquid-level data acquisition system. Liquid-level data is interfaced via I2C. Additionally, it can be mounted to the sensor slot of the WisBlock Base board.
parent_content: RAK12059 is a WisBlock Liquid Level Sensor module that extends the WisBlock system with a Liquid Level Sensor from MILONE. Additionally, it can be mounted to the sensor slot of the WisBlock Base board.

title: RAK12059 WisBlock Liquid Level Sensor > RAK12059 WisBlock Liquid Level Sensor > Prerequisites > RAK12059 Module Requirements and Setup
content:
To use a **RAK12059**, you need at least a **WisBlock Base** to plug the module in. **WisBlock Base** provides power supply to the **RAK12059** module. Furthermore, you need a **WisBlock Core** module to use the sensor.  
> **WARNING:** Make sure to fix the module with the screws to ensure a proper function.
